Supporting the Wellbeing of International and Domestic Students

A Contemporary Tool For Providing Support

With the developing impact of the current social and economic circumstances, many students are experiencing elevated stress and anxiety in both academic and personal environments. For many institutions, the desire to offer assistance with the self-management of such issues has led to the development of our new self service software platform, Healthy Me Anonymous.

Healthy Me Anonymous offers users a simple and interactive platform to access digital resources based on their specific situation or requirements. The application is de-identified for the user, and is interfaced with a powerful reporting tool for the identification of critical management statistics for users of the app such as demographics and resources being accessed.
